hey believe the person can make the decision without their help</li>\n  <li>it goes against a decision made by an attorney acting under a Lasting Power of Attorney</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Deputies can&rsquo;t:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>restrain the person, unless it&rsquo;s to stop them coming to harm</li>\n  <li>stop life-sustaining medical treatment, eg turn off a life-support machine</li>\n  <li>make a will for the person, or change their existing will</li>\n  <li>make large gifts out of the person&rsquo;s money</li>\n  <li>hold any money or property in their own name on the person&rsquo;s behalf</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>However, a deputy can use the <a href=\"/court-funds-office-processes\" title=\"Court Funds Office\">Court Funds Office</a>, or a bank or building society account to help someone with their finances.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Download <a href=\"http://www.justice.gov.uk/global/forms/opg/deputies/index.htm\" title=\"Forms and guidance for deputies appointed by the Court of Protection\" rel=\"external\">forms and guidance for deputies appointed by the Court of Protection.</a></p>\n</div>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-deputy/apply-to-become-a-deputy","slug":"apply-to-become-a-deputy","order":3,"title":"Apply to become a deputy","body":"<p>If you want to apply to become a deputy, <a href=\"/find-someones-attorney-or-deputy\" title=\"check if the person already has a deputy or attorney\">check if the person already has a deputy or attorney</a> acting on their behalf.</p>\n\n<p>If they don&rsquo;t, you can <a href=\"/apply-to-the-court-of-protection\" title=\"apply to the Court of Protection\">apply to the Court of Protection</a> to become their deputy. </p>\n\n<p>If the court approves your application, they will send you a court order appointing you as a deputy. </p>\n\n<p>The court order will explain what decisions you&rsquo;re legally allowed to make.</p>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-deputy/reports-and-supervisio