quo;attorney&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<p>When choosing an attorney, think about:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>how well the person looks after their own affairs, eg their finances</li>\n  <li>how well you know them</li>\n  <li>if you trust them to make decisions in your best interests</li>\n  <li>how happy they will be to make decisions for you</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Who can be your attorney</h2>\n\n<p>Your attorney can be anyone 18 or over, eg:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>a relative</li>\n  <li>a friend</li>\n  <li>a professional (like a solicitor)</li>\n  <li>your husband, wife or partner</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Who can&rsquo;t be your attorney</h2>\n\n<p>You can&rsquo;t choose someone who:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>is under 18</li>\n  <li>is unable to make decisions</li>\n  <li>is <a href=\"/bankruptcy/when-does-bankruptcy-end\" title=\"Bankruptcy: when does bankruptcy end\">currently bankrupt</a> (if you want them to look after property or money)</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/power-of-attorney/make-a-lasting-power-of-attorney","slug":"make-a-lasting-power-of-attorney","order":3,"title":"Make a Lasting Power of Attorney","body":"<h2>Read the guidance</h2>\n\n<p>Read the guidance on making a Lasting Power of Attorney and filling in the forms.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-guidance-health-and-welfare.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF 1.32MB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney’ (PDF, 1.32MB)</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-guidance-property-affairs.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF, 1.35MB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney’ (PDF, 1.35MB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Download the forms</h2>\n\n<h3>Health and